Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:02.38,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,At a summer beach far away from Academy City,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:04.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kamijo Touma, am having a reunion with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.36,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A magic spell known as "Angel Fall" has befallen us though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.57,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Misha Croitsef of the Russian Orthodox Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:14.03,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and Tsuchimikado Motoharu,\Nwho appeared with Kanzaki Kaori,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:17.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,also a member of Necessarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...Wait, what?!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.30,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.64,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a member of Necessarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:10.81,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Necessarius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.40,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.19,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:14.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.73,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no way a magician can be in Academy City", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.28,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.88,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,"Science" and "magic" are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:30.12,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Then an agent or two sneaking into enemy territory... isn't that shocking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.57,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Agent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:34.02,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,A spy, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.42,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I know of most things surrounding you, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.75,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I know about Imagine Breaker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:47.53,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, having gone through a lot of the\Nesper curriculum, much of my magic is unusable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:53.97,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there is a high probability that\Nthe spellcaster of Angel Fall is hiding near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.89,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The same could apply to the ritual location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:01.79,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We should move together for now and investigate the enemy's objective and their next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.32,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any objections, Misha Croitsef?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:09.07,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Answer no. 1 - That should be the most intelligent strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.32,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:14.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with family members that I haven't seen in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My parents and cousin are at the hotel-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:21.25,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Do your parents and cousin appear like they should to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.76,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Some charm you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:36.88,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.31,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Replicas have some power enchanted in them, too, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.94,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The basic principle in idol worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you're a magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.99,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,"Were", it's past tense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:58.54,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The best Onmyo professor of Necessarius who specialized in Feng Hsui is now just a plain old human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to join the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.87,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:10.61,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,When Angel Fall was activated, Kanzaki-neechin and I cast seals on ourselves right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.97,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't get away from it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.45,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From the eyes of everyone that "switched sides",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.59,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hitotsui Hajime apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.31,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotsui Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, that shallow idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.56,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who's Kanzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:30.30,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,My... Touma's friends are really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.61,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Oniisan, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.26,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Red hair and a cigarette in your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.24,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,And a bar code on your cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.95,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,How do you say this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.21,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say he's dandy, right, Aunt Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.34,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.42,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.46,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a charm from Egypt for you all-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.67,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the scarabs, Uncle Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.63,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.26,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.97,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She's Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you just said you cast a seal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't espers unable to use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:09.32,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why I'm messed up all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.47,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,If I use magic again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.36,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,my blood vessels will burst, and *bang*
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.41,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be dead for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.96,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.91,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Your "such misfortune" favorite phrase,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.87,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,try not to say it in front of Neechin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.65,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Opposite to your misfortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.92,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Neechin is a person that can't tolerate her own fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.76,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tolerate her own fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:38.27,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan, there's an organization called Amakusa-shiki, founded by Christians hiding in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:44.19,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,It was determined that Kanzaki-neechin was to be the top of that organization, the Priestess, at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:49.04,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of only a few "Saints" in this world capable of wielding a Stigma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:53.65,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,A Saint, in other words, a human that can harness the power of the son of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:06:00.70,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,When she unleashes her Stigma, Neechin is able to temporarily wield power greater than that of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.83,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,She apparently can't forgive herself for being born with that much fortune and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.23,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Great, "God" again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:11.05,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that a worry for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.18,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,That's something only she would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.01,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.26,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,How do fortunate people feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:25.21,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To always be drawing the one and only winning lottery ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.19,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...means you're always going to have others draw the losing tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.11,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.95,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.70,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...because of the effects of Angel Fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So I heard, your appearance is Style, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.83,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.22,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take a bath to relieve my fatigue,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.05,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,but if someone comes in while I'm in the ladies' bath, panic will ensue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.14,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And you also have a problem if someone goes into the men's bath, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.25,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,So, please stand watch for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.85,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure no one comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.90,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.06,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked you this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.05,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It's a taboo phrase in front of Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.12,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:48.90,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.15,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.63,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take a bath together, father and son, like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:55.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.68,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.83,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hot spring; that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.70,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.54,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.77,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to be embarrassed, we're grown men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.79,index alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah- That is- Really... It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.71,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:25.41,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, red-haired, cigarette-chewing, bar-code cheeked Kanzaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:30.58,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:35.09,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Forgetting your gratitude just because he saw your naked body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.51,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan is the one we are indebted to for saving Index's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.92,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank him, we should,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.74,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,but chasing him out of the bath area, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.25,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.21,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.69,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your friend is really, really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:05.05,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,For him to be panicking so much even though we're all men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.62,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of reasons behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:08.85,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.12,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he really swings "that" way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.81,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,that he can't marry anymore because I saw his naked body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.39,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fantasizing about things the wrong way already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.28,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That everyone's appearance has switched due to Angel Fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...means that the appearance of Dad\Nis really the face of some stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.60,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.96,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You seem all depressed all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.84,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.80,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That face of yours looks just like your mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.91,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Before we got married, when we were having dates every now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.06,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,as the time came for us to part ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.73,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,your mother would always have that look on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.53,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't bear seeing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.61,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,...but I found it so darling, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.86,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You take after your mother more after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.60,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, here's a souvenir from Mexico-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.25,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Misha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.34,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,The gloominess on such an innocent child's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.51,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she wants us to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.89,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.49,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:56.41,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a bit homesick since Russia, the land of Tsundere, is so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:56.41,Note,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Note: This is a pun on Tundra (tsundora) and Tsundere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.31,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She's not responding to the joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:04.67,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Does this woman understand the emptiness when a joke gets ignored?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.34,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:25.53,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out anything about Angel Fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:31.74,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I don't understand much about this angel business,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.20,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,but why did the suspect activate this kind of spell to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:41.38,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Hypothesis no. 1 - To acquire the vast amount of power an angel possesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.75,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Or to become part of the angel class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.51,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Fall is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.18,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.94,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,The power of an angel is strong enough to destroy the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.98,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,If Angel Fall were completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.90,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,a calamity as great as those of lore would take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:11.70,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,We must identify the spellcaster before that and prevent the completion of the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.37,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.52,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be chewing on gum, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.45,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,World crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.80,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Touya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.23,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:31.97,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, what are you getting all energetic about, Touya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.97,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Touma's face brought back a lot of memories, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:40.29,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought he'd like a brother or sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.19,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.22,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Misha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.42,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Before the world's crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take care of another, personal one right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:50.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.26,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.17,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.35,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What time are you barging in-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:59.55,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Touma-san, you want to sleep together with the whole family again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:03.04,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let us sleep like the "Kawa" kanji tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:05.78,Note,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Kawa 川 - Where the child (shortest stroke) sleeps in between the two parents (longer strokes)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.76,index,!Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma! Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.19,index,!Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma's not in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.09,index,!Index,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't come back since last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:23.68,index,!Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.92,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.17,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on; it's still so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in such a haste...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.41,index,!Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.80,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.71,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to lock the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.13,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back and lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.25,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a whole day there-and-back by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.09,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back by evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:56.04,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Question no. 1 - May I accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Misha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:01.18,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating question no. 1 - May I accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:06.15,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Misha-chan. You want to give me some company along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.87,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.95,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Misha have to accompany Ind- Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.24,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.08,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You were her first, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.34,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she has to become your bride now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.01,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,...and she's trying to score points with her future mother-in-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.88,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.89,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You two were in a good mood last night, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.08,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You were peeking, you perverted father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.10,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, if you were watching, couldn't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.02,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.90,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a rather modest girl; a rarity these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.32,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,She tried not to touch your hand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.15,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.66,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My... right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.45,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Fall is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.93,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,If Angel Fall were completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.71,index,Misha,0000,0000,0000,,a calamity as great as those of lore would take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.13,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Misha said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:19.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so we don't really know\Nthe actual form of Angel Fall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.55,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.15,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't even a record in the British Library,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.56,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,a completely unknown phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:30.10,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, how does she know if such a thing is incomplete or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.32,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That a calamity would occur if it were completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...why is Misha able to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:44.37,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Misha not touch my right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:46.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she was a bit shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.63,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...she cast the spell herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:56.84,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...and didn't want the in-progress spell of Angel Fall to be erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.33,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan! Take us to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:01.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.85,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? A map to our home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.53,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We moved, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Draw me a map to our new home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.38,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,Why all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.98,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go after Mom or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.85,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.82,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.20,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want Mom stealing Misha-chan away from you-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.28,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fantasizing in such an unreasonable fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.15,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and hurry!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.49,index,Touya,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming Misha cast Angel Fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.84,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,why is she after Index, I mean, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.51,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:40.30,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to ask Misha personally to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.15,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This... is my home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.73,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Misha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.74,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait for their arrival here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:05.93,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.13,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad sure goes crazy in his souvenir mania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.99,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's... my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.62,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:58.79,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.59,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.55,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.60,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on, Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I said, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.36,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This... is my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:26.61,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.70,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,This was a photo from New Year last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.12,index,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me now, Touma-oniichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.63,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.35,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's appearance didn't get switched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:55.73,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The only person that isn't affected by Angel Fall, besides exceptions like you, Kami-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.19,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...is the spellcaster himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.65,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.65,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.90,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,My, Hitotsui Hajime!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.15,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.99,index,Shiina,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a big fan of yours!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.10,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:29.80,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot what Misha tried to do to you when she thought you were the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.60,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're able to do something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you put your hands into the occult world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.27,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going, damn it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.39,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna die or somethin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-Himegami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.20,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta the way already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.71,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna flatten 'ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.79,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,What the-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.00,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.52,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look like a damn taxi cab to you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.09,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's... My father's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:12.76,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.60,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.95,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,This brings me to tears, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.65,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,A child who pays tribute to his parents is so rare these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:27.65,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.17,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Buckle up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.82,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pick you up if you get thrown out of the window, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.95,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:37.16,index,!Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, move it, move it, move it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.66,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.66,index alt,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Misha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.10,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Misha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:01.18,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you two go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.31,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Touya is on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.61,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:11.86,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.66,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You must wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.87,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,This is my job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.19,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I will secure Mr. Touya's-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.25,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:26.79,index,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.21,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo Touya is my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.76,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,My one and only... father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:27.91,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The emergence of a terrible entity that surpasses the world of human knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:29.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,a power that's set out to destroy the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and Kanzaki, who is standing against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.00,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And Tsuchimikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Power of God".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:37.51,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
